Package org.escoladeltreball.ulisesmap.activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseActivity
    BaseActivity Handle a option menu used in almost all activities which allow to a user personalize a view of route on the map.
    LoginActivity
    LoginActivity Activity that enables the user to log on.
    MapActivity
    MapActivity Show a route from an array of points according to chosen option in menu.
    MenuActivity
    MenuActivity Show a menu with the different options.
    RegisterActivity
    RegisterActivity Activity that register new user in database
    ShowCommentsActivity
    ShowCommentActivity Show all comments and ratings.
    ShowPointsActivity
    ShowPointsActivity Show all points of city and go to MapActivity
    ShowRoutesActivity
    ShowRoutesActivity Show all routes available for chosen city
    UlisesActivity
    Main activity which show animated text with name of application and animated logo
